  			<div id="item-1777"><p>Sue, if you read my original <a href="http://technically.us/eat/articles/2006/03/23/favorite-meat-loaf">recipe</a> you will see why I don&#8217;t like to use a loaf pan to cook my meatloaf in, but I suppose that&#8217;s just a matter of individual taste&#8212;I like the crust brown and crispy all the way down the sides and I think using a loaf pan prevents that. I like your idea of saut√©eing the onions and green peppers first, though. I&#8217;ll have to try that next time.</p></div>
